{"tid":1316464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日講民意民意，個運動係你架，真係需要人點睇咩？","createTime":"2019-07-14T16:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T18:30:12.000Z","uid":78217,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e263f484d254b4430b11fef7c910f9945aaf0ce1","tid":1316464,"uid":78217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"成日講民意，講嚟做咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再咁落去個運動會綁手綁腳，人地點睇咪由佢<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做，<br />\n出面班人點睇，咪由佢點睇，<br />\n<br />\n你有必要改變自己去感化佢地？<br />\n<br />\n就算今日俾你感化到，<br />\n班人第二日就會轉風向去屌返你地，<br />\n咁到時點呀？<br />\n又改變多次自己去迎合個班人？<br />\n<br />\n你睇出面，d人真係想殺咗你，<br />\n你仲要好似d戰俘舉高手，由佢殺？<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們，我地要反抗，<br />\n「士可殺，不可辱」"},{"pid":"755720484cc90a7baf4a2439f9e7a112d62e18cb","tid":1316464,"uid":135274,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:07:30.000Z","msg":"群眾運動點會唔需要民意啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你需要既係操控民意（負責洗白、帶風向）而唔係俾民意綁住你本身既行動姐"},{"pid":"f9c2cbcaa35dae4c7b54760430f3a851f762e84c","tid":1316464,"uid":78217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9233e3d7eba0a88dc51eb4b0de5e17e44bdc5350","tid":1316464,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:08:40.000Z","msg":"［純紓發］我們缺乏了什麼？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"03281acec7dbd53444e25b8e017b4b21f6e5ca3b","tid":1316464,"uid":78217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"755720484cc90a7baf4a2439f9e7a112d62e18cb","tid":1316464,"uid":135274,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:07:30.000Z","msg":"群眾運動點會唔需要民意啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你需要既係操控民意（負責洗白、帶風向）而唔係俾民意綁住你本身既行動姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"你講得岩，但有時民意係雙面刃，